                "_id": {

                },
                "name": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "email": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "movie_id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                },
                "text": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "date": {
                    "bsonType": "date"
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": true,
            "required": [
                "_id",

                "email",
                "movie_id",
                "text",
                "date"

        }
    },
